title: ELEMENT 'SACRAMENTO' MAKE IT COUNT - 2012 INTERNATIONAL SKATE CONTEST SERIES
description:
Miika Adamov was the overall winner of the 2012 MAKE IT COUNT Contest at Epic Skatepark in Sacramento, CA. Miika will join contest winners from all over the world at the finals at Element YMCA Camp in August, along with a trip to The Berrics. The next MAKE IT COUNT Contest will be in New England on February 25th.

ZONE 1
13 & Under - Connor Kepp
14 & Up/Sponsored - Bradley Elias

ZONE 2
13 & Under - Andrew Chesmore
14 & Up/Sponsored - Fernando Rios

ZONE 3
13 & Under - Jake Kottke
14 & Up/Sponsored - Miika Adamov

HIGH OLLIE BAR CHAMP
Tyler Elsey (39")

OVERALL WINNER
Miika Adamov

Music by: 
Loren Humphrey
"Two For Two"
